# Force LF on scripts. The Workflow tool reads workflows/*.js via scriptPath and shows
# them in an approval dialog that rejects a raw CR (\r) as a hidden control character,
# so a CRLF checkout (default on Windows) makes every scriptPath launch fail. Also keeps
# hook scripts and the POSIX test harness LF regardless of platform.
*.js   text eol=lf
*.mjs  text eol=lf
*.sh   text eol=lf
